    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color:#555555;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75">
      Safety Harbor homeowners trust Happy Roof for quality roof replacement, repair, and installation. Nestled along Old Tampa Bay with a charming downtown district and the iconic Safety Harbor Resort & Spa, this city deserves a roofing contractor that matches its character. As a licensed and insured roofing contractor, we deliver roofing systems engineered for Florida's coastal conditions — backed by our 15-year workmanship warranty.
