<!-- WHY HAPPY ROOF IN SAFETY HARBOR -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Happy Roof in Safety Harbor</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY SAFETY HARBOR HOMEOWNERS CHOOSE HAPPY ROOF</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          Safety Harbor is one of Pinellas County's best-kept secrets — a small city with a big personality, anchored by the historic Safety Harbor Resort & Spa and a walkable downtown district filled with local shops, galleries, and restaurants. The tree-lined residential streets feature a mix of mid-century ranch homes, updated bungalows, and newer construction, each with its own roofing needs shaped by proximity to Old Tampa Bay and the unique microclimate that comes with waterfront living.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          Homes along Bayshore Boulevard and the streets surrounding Philippe Park face direct bay exposure — meaning stronger winds during storms, elevated humidity, and salt air that accelerates wear on roofing materials. Inland Safety Harbor neighborhoods are more sheltered but still contend with Florida's brutal UV radiation, heavy summer downpours, and the ever-present threat of hurricane-season winds. Happy Roof understands these conditions because we work in them every day.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          We hold Florida Roofing Contractor License #CCC1337380, carry full general liability and workers' compensation insurance, and pull all required permits with the City of Safety Harbor and Pinellas County. Whether your home overlooks Old Tampa Bay from Bayshore Boulevard or sits on a quiet cul-de-sac near the downtown district, we deliver the same standard of quality and stand behind every installation with a 15-year workmanship warranty in writing.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">15-Year Workmanship Warranty</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every Safety Harbor roof we install comes with a written 15-year workmanship warranty — no exceptions, no fine print.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Pinellas County Permits Handled</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We pull all required permits with the City of Safety Harbor and Pinellas County and coordinate every inspection from start to finish.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES IN SAFETY HARBOR -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Our Services</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">ROOFING SERVICES WE OFFER IN SAFETY HARBOR</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Roof Replacement</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">
          Full tear-off and replacement using Owens Corning Duration HDZ shingles, standing seam metal panels, or concrete and clay tile. Safety Harbor's many mid-century homes often benefit from a complete roof system upgrade including modern underlayment and improved ventilation. We handle decking inspection, flashing, and every permit and county inspection. Most shingle roofs are completed in 1 to 3 days.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Roof Repair</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">
          From missing shingles and cracked tile to damaged flashing around chimneys and skylights, we diagnose and repair roofing issues throughout Safety Harbor. Bay-side homes along Bayshore Boulevard are especially susceptible to wind-driven rain intrusion and flashing failures. We respond quickly after storms and provide honest assessments — if a repair is all you need, that is what we recommend.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4"/><polyline points="16 17 21 12 16 7"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="9" y2="12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Storm Damage & Insurance</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">
          Safety Harbor's position on Old Tampa Bay places it in a high-risk zone during tropical storms and hurricanes. When storms hit, we provide thorough damage assessments, document everything for your insurance claim, and coordinate directly with your adjuster. We work with all major insurance carriers in Florida and guide Safety Harbor homeowners through the entire claims process.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR PROCESS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">How It Works</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">OUR 4-STEP PROCESS</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Free Inspection & Estimate</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We inspect your roof from top to bottom — checking decking, underlayment, flashing, ventilation, and overall condition. You receive a detailed written estimate with material options, timelines, and transparent pricing. No pressure, no hidden fees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Material Selection & Permits</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Choose your roofing material and color with our guidance. We pull all permits with the City of Safety Harbor or Pinellas County, order materials from the manufacturer, and schedule installation on a date that works for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Professional Installation</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Our crew performs the full tear-off, inspects and repairs decking as needed, installs new underlayment and flashing, and lays your new roofing system to manufacturer specifications. We protect your landscaping, driveway, and property throughout the process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Final Inspection & Warranty</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We schedule the county inspection to verify code compliance. Once passed, you receive your warranty documentation — including our 15-year workmanship warranty and manufacturer material warranty. We follow up at 30 days and 1 year.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICE AREA -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Safety Harbor Service Area</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1rem">NEIGHBORHOODS WE SERVE IN SAFETY HARBOR</h2>
      <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto">Happy Roof provides roofing services throughout Safety Harbor and the surrounding communities in central Pinellas County. From the bayfront to the suburbs, we have you covered.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Downtown District</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Bayshore Blvd</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Philippe Park</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Marshall Street</span>
