      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Common Questions</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">SAFETY HARBOR ROOFING FAQ</h2>
