    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        How much does a roof replacement cost in Safety Harbor?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Roof replacement costs in Safety Harbor typically range from $8,000 to $25,000+ depending on your roof's size, pitch, material choice (shingles, metal, or tile), and whether structural repairs are needed. Homes along Bayshore Boulevard and near the Old Tampa Bay waterfront may have additional considerations due to wind exposure and older construction. Happy Roof provides free, detailed estimates with no hidden fees — call <a href="tel:8135957663" class="call-tracking-number" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">(813) 595-7663</a> for a personalized quote.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        What roofing materials work best for Safety Harbor's waterfront location?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Safety Harbor sits on the western shore of Old Tampa Bay, which means homes face salt air exposure, strong bay winds, and Florida's intense UV radiation. Standing seam metal roofing resists corrosion and lasts 40–60 years. Owens Corning Duration HDZ shingles rated for 130+ MPH winds are popular throughout Safety Harbor's residential neighborhoods. Tile roofs are a great match for the craftsman and Mediterranean-style homes found near the downtown district and along Philippe Park.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        Does Happy Roof handle permits for Safety Harbor roofing projects?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
