        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Most Safety Harbor shingle roof replacements are completed in 1 to 3 days. Metal roofs typically take 3 to 5 days, and tile roofs may require 5 to 7 days depending on complexity. Florida's summer afternoon thunderstorms can occasionally cause brief delays, but we plan around weather and keep you updated at every stage of the project.</div>
