        Is Happy Roof licensed to work in Safety Harbor?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. Happy Roof LLC holds Florida Roofing Contractor License #CCC1337380, which authorizes roofing work throughout the entire state of Florida — including the City of Safety Harbor and all of Pinellas County. We carry full general liability and workers' compensation insurance, and certificates are available upon request.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
